{"tid":2518254,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"當年BOMBA影片收費被怒反，現今YOUTUBE會員制影片無人出聲","createTime":"2021-05-06T01:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-06T02:50:19.000Z","uid":250308,"like":43,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"9683ecd855f98c3426b2c26f49bf92c907ee703c","tid":2518254,"uid":250308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T01:50:56.000Z","msg":"是否可悲? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當年BOMBO 8蚊一條片計劃被吠到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果當年YOUTUBE一早有會員收費影片設置<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後BOMBA將D本來想收費既片放係會員專區<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該就無人出聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話晒BOMBA都有幾十萬訂閱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果只有一萬人訂閱收費專區，以5美金一位咁計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每個月都50000美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係40萬港幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n8蚊一條片冇人想比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊個想比，我都唔想比，比左唔知值唔值<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但5美金睇一個月好易引到人課，5美金任睇WOR<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔洗整臭個朵，又可以明正言順收費<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同一種效果，同一個目標，但唔同方式，唔同模式。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就已經令到班網民冇晒聲出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBOMBA主力POINT其實相當合理，同伍公子集資買耳機概念差不多，拍片係要成本，YOUTUBER都要搵食，搵食姐，犯法呀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算唔犯法，就算合情合理，但人類係一種容易被人洗腦既生物，只要你既方式錯左，無論你講乜，都係聽唔入耳，然後不斷搵理由去批評<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個係人性探討，唔係幫任何人平反，BOMBA都係抵死既，本身就唔好笑，仲收費<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇咁大個頭，就唔好戴咁大頂帽，等其他人行左收費呢步先跟風都未遲，急住想憑個DD名氣搵錢，咪奶野囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d6ff769fc319f7b5f2a78da7a24ced836eec145","tid":2518254,"uid":13147,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"9683ecd855f98c3426b2c26f49bf92c907ee703c","tid":2518254,"uid":250308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T01:50:56.000Z","msg":"是否可悲? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當年BOMBO 8蚊一條片計劃被吠到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果當年YOUTUBE一早有會員收費影片設置<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後BOMBA將D本來想收費既片放係會員專區<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該就無人出聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話晒BOMBA都有幾十萬訂閱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果只有一萬人訂閱收費專區，以5美金一位咁計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每個月都50000美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係40萬港幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n8蚊一條片冇人想比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊個想比，我都唔想比，比左唔知值唔值<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但5美金睇一個月好易引到人課，5美金任睇WOR<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔洗整臭個朵，又可以明正言順收費<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同一種效果，同一個目標，但唔同方式，唔同模式。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就已經令到班網民冇晒聲出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBOMBA主力POINT其實相當合理，同伍公子集資買耳機概念差不多，拍片係要成本，YOUTUBER都要搵食，搵食姐，犯法呀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" clas