ass=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T02:36:15.000Z","msg":"問題睇既然youtube都有會員制功能<br />\n點解唔放入會員影片限定?<br />\n<br />\n而且唔係個個都有信用卡, 呢個情況咪可以用google Play Card"},{"pid":"faa357ec32c1a2383d275865c86fe156a4ae2faf","tid":2518254,"uid":289900,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b43a2219dabdbf332255f98c52815f1eef41ff3a","tid":2518254,"uid":41411,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T02:05:21.000Z","msg":"伍公仔叫人sponsor耳機=伍乞衣<br />\n而家個個開live都叫人donate, 又有membership<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T02:37:41.000Z","msg":"道尼拾階咗未"},{"pid":"3038da8d344c96ec9ddac0f877e5a6d9fd16d0cf","tid":2518254,"uid":377175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b95759909110e8c7050924f51da1803940a0d194","tid":2518254,"uid":176303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8d6ff769fc319f7b5f2a78da7a24ced836eec145","tid":2518254,"uid":13147,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"9683ecd855f98c3426b2c26f49bf92c907ee703c","tid":2518254,"uid":250308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T01:50:56.000Z","msg":"是否可悲? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當年BOMBO 8蚊一條片計劃被吠到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果當年YOUTUBE一早有會員收費影片設置<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後BOMBA將D本來想收費既片放係會員專區<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該就無人出聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話晒BOMBA都有幾十萬訂閱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果只有一萬人訂閱收費專區，以5美金一位咁計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每個月都50000美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係40萬港幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n8蚊一條片冇人想比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊個想比，我都唔想比，比左唔知值唔值<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但5美金睇一個月好易引到人課，5美金任睇WOR<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔洗整臭個朵，又可以明正言順收費<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同一種效果，同一個目標，但唔同方式，唔同模式。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就已經令到班網民冇晒聲出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBOMBA主力POINT其實相當合理，同伍公子集資買耳機概念差不多，拍片係要成本，YOUTUBER都要搵食，搵食姐，犯法呀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算唔犯法，就算合情合理，但人類係一種容易被人洗腦既生物，只要你既方式錯左，無論你講乜，都係聽唔入耳，然後不斷搵理由去批評<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個係人性探討，唔係幫任何人平反，BOMBA都係抵死既，本身就唔好笑，仲收費<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇咁大個頭，就唔好戴咁大頂帽，等其他人行左收費呢步先跟風都未遲，急住想憑個DD名氣搵錢，咪奶野囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T01:52:04.000Z","msg":"BOMBA係？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T02:22:41.000Z","msg":"講真   之前吹到好多人細細個開始睇佢<br />\n我反而係佢話復出我先識佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T02:37:44.000Z","msg":"真心咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係因為佢先睇youtube<br />\n之後先識熊仔頭（ 唔知邊個歷史耐啲但係我係睇幫bomba先)<br />\n咁以前香港youtuber未咁普及嘅時候 <br />\n你睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55467e6bdc0a1dc63f5c81d940526e93086230e5","tid":2518254,"uid":121548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T02:38:06.000Z","msg":"成班小學雞係到盲反"},{"pid":"860da34e165752eb01c456d51cd28630065309e4","tid":2518254,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T02:38:52.000Z","